content: have been an insomniac with anxiety most of my adult life. I loved this app previously, now that it's changed, it's not even l ½ of what it used to be 😔
I've just this app for years, absolutely love it. One thing I would love though is the option just to play the music as that's sooo relaxing

I love all of the Andrew Johnson apps I've tried so far! I started using them about 7 years ago at the recommendation of my M.E specialist occupational therapist to help with relaxation and sleep. The power nap and deep sleep are currently my favourite and I'm hoping to try some more of the others! If you've not tried hypnotherapy before this could be a good way to gently ease you in if you're thinking about having live therapy sessions (which I have had an also recommend!!).
Ever since the update i haven't been able to use the application properly as the soundtrack plays for 2 minutes then it stops
This app was great, but since the update, it plays 8 hours of music after the session, keeping me awake. It's now unusable.
Had this for years now all says is, hi this is Andrew, and goes back to beginning. Won't play. Restarted phone and uninstalled his app and reinstalled still will not play.
Very good, great night's sleep. Only thing is I wish there was a way to disable the background music. The "crinkle tinkles" are loud.

The older version was so much better. In this one he talks way too much rubbish and it's distracting. It doesn't help me sleep at all, it just leaves me feeling frustrated and wishing for the older version that actually helped me relax and sleep. DON'T WASTE YOUR MONEY ON THIS!

After a recent Android update, these apps crash after 10 secs. Email to developer not replied to. I have uninstalled and reinstalled twice. Still crashes. These are apps I purchased. Would not recommend for Android.
Suddenly stopped working have uninstalled & reinstalled. Still crashes 5 seconds in

Edit: The 11:26 is the intro, it keeps going after that ends, according to your settings. This app is the first thing I install on a new phone, I've loved it for years now. It has helped me cope with unmanaged insomnia, chronic pain, and severe migraines. I often just rewind the initial relaxation intro if I don't fall asleep the first time. He has a lovely soothing voice, with a pleasant Scots accent, and the guidance is just what I need to calm my racing ADHD brain during times of distress.

I need to sleep now. I always relied on this recording but its different now. I dont recognize it and the process is different. Idk what I'm going to do to sleep tonight. I'm used to listening to this but now I cant.
Try it.. you will know the difference..
need to listen nightly for at least 3-4 weeks at a time,but not sporadically
Andrews voice is very soothing

Have had this app for years, we refer to it as "the Scotsman". When I want to get to sleep fast, when I'm having trouble getting to sleep or wake up and can't back to sleep. "Let's use the Scotsman?" Love it.

No no no no no no I have used this app for years and I have gotten used to the order working from bottom to top, you can't totally flip it around!! Please go back to how it was before, I can't sleep to this anymore 😭
I used to love this app but I need the old version back for it to work. Please add the old version as an option to listen to.

Andrew Johnson is the greatest. I've been listening to his recordings for years and they have had a huge impact on my well being. I have to agree with others reviewers about the update. It's now all too short. The length of his inductions were part of what made his hypnosis work so well.

I have this app, I would fall asleep fast. Since the update it's so short and disappointing.

Sometimes I don't even last after he tells you to focus on your feet. I feel so much better after I listen to it. Sleeping could never be made easier. I am in school and it makes it a perfect way to fall asleep at 10 each night and feel 100% ready to face the day. Update: its like 3 or 4 years later and i have yet to find a better app to help me sleep.

I LOVED this and many of Andrew's apps. But the new update changed one thing that I do not like. If the session is repeated... There's a new part where his voice is louder and woke me up every time it played... Before I wanted it to wake me. I love the new look of the app but can I have the old version back????? Please????

I've been using this app and loved it for years now but since the update it's a load of rubbish. Andrews voice is so soothing and lulls me off to sleep but it takes a bit of time, so I put it on repeat. Now that he only speaks for a few minutes and then it's just music, I no longer fade off into deep sleep, because when the repeat starts, suddenly he speaks again and it wakes me right up. Very disappointed, please revert it back to the way it was before the update, no longer works for me.
I have been using this app for years and it has worked well. The new update ruined a great app, the speech seems to have been lessened and replaced by music

I've had this app for years now, and have loved it and recommend to many, but recent update has changed a lot. At first I thought it was just the look of the app and that's fine with me, but I actually think there is a now less content, it's only about 7mins long, and though you can put on repeat, previously it was far longer and no need to repeat

I have been using this app to sleep for the past 8 and a half years! I can't sleep without hearing that relaxing voice! EVERY SINGLE NIGHT FOR 8.5 YEARS! I love the update app! It's so cute and much easier to use. I love the breathing blob!

I love Andrew Johnson's app and have used 3 different ones. I was very dissapointed tonight when I went to use it and the script was different. I was so conditioned to the old script that I would fall asleep very quickly. Is there any way to go back to the old script? It's still good but I really liked the other one.
Love this app. Have used it lots. Really helps with getting to sleep
Excellent gets better every time I use it.

Updating this app would be life-changing.

Always puts me and my daughter (12yrs) to sleep.

You get fresh new content and a meditation leader that suits you as well, or a variety if you prefer. Purely a waste of money if you ask me.

Andrew Johnson's methods are far more powerful, in the gentlest way possible (in my opinion). This review applies to all of his apps - those I've recently downloaded, and am looking forward to trying now.

Please consider a chronic pain meditation for my husband! Thanks!

I am an autistic adult. I suffer profoundly from insomnia. It has been a month of personal tragedy and last night at 3am, after being awake for two days, I was desperate.   I read the reviews and figured that I threw out a stale bag of chips the night before that had cost the same, what harm could it do?   At first, I admit, I had a smile from ear to ear listening to this lovely Scottish brogue. I was so doubtful that my mind would quiet. I checked at 3:12, and figured that at least I was relaxed, so that was an improvement.   Then I pulled of my night mask and the sun was out. I had managed to sleep until 8:45.  Thank you, dreamy Scottish man for rocking my incessant brain to sleep. I plan on following the instructions and continuing nightly for three weeks.

I suffer with insomnia, caused by stress and anxiety. This app is the only thing that's actually worked for me, even medication didn't work. Thanks so much you've helped me get my life back on track before this my sleeping pattern was a mess and I was putting my degree in jeopardy because I wasn't awake during day hours. This app takes my mind off all the thoughts spinning around my head and actually makes me focus on relaxing and sleeping.THANK YOU.
